Company Profile




						> About Us / 
						Company Profile /
					


	Solomon Systech Limited is a leading semiconductor company providing display IC products and system solutions on an international basis under its own global brand. Adopting a "fabless" business model, the Group specializes in the design, development and sales of proprietary IC products that enable a wide range of display applications for smartphones, smart TVs and other smart devices including consumer electronics products, wearables, portable devices and industrial appliances.  

	 

	The Group has a high caliber and experienced design team to develop its own Intellectual Properties (IP) for highly integrated display IC products and total system solutions, including:

	 


		Mobile Display Driver IC (DDI) & In-Cell Touch Display Driver IC (TDDI)


			maXTouch® On-Cell & Out-Cell Touch Controller IC


		MIPI Bridge IC

		Display Controller IC 

		Large DDI 

		OLED DDI

		Bistable DDI

		OLED Lighting Driver IC 



	Given a design team with in-depth experience, senior management personnel of over twenty years of experience in the global semiconductor industry, a broad product portfolio covering nearly all kinds of display technologies; and dedicated design centers in different regions plus a worldwide sales and distribution network, Solomon Systech has become one of the major display IC suppliers in the world, supporting global customers with proprietary display IC products and total system solutions.

	 

	The Group serves many blue-chip clients and has received numerous awards from its customers, suppliers, industrial organizations as well as the investment community. The Group's shares were listed on the Main Board of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited on 8 April 2004 (HKSE: 2878).

	 

Corporate Backgrounder

	 

	The Group has two key business units, namely Main Display and Advanced Display. The Main Display business focuses on mainstream display solutions including Mobile Touch, Mobile Driver, Mobile Interface, as well as Large Display products. The Advanced Display business includes OLED Display and Lighting products, as well as Bistable Display products.

	 










