Introduction
Founded in 1999, Solomon Systech Limited is a leading semiconductor company providing display IC products and system solutions on an international basis under its own global brand. Adopting a “fabless” business model, the Group specializes in the design, development and sales of proprietary IC products and system solutions that enable a wide range of display applications for smartphones, smart TVs and other smart devices including consumer electronics products, portable devices, industrial appliances and green energy applications. 

Solomon Systech (International) Limited’s shares have been listed on the main board of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited since April 8th, 2004 (stock code: 2878).


Product
Solomon Systech provides high performance, high resolution and cost-effective display IC products and system solutions through four business units, including:

Mobile Display
- TFT LCD Driver IC, TFT In-Cell Touch LCD Driver IC and STN LCD Driver IC targeting smartphones, smart watches, GPS, printers, etc.

Mobile System
- Capacitive Touch Panel Controller IC (Out-cell, In-cell, On-cell), MIPI Display Interface Controller IC, Display Controller IC, Graphic Controller IC, 3D Image Processor Controller IC, Complete System Solution (i.e. SoC + Software + Applications), Development Kit. Key applications include smartphones, smart watches, tablets, laptops, cameras, personal navigation devices, gaming devices, etc.

Advanced Display
- PMOLED Driver IC, AMOLED Driver IC and Bistable Display Driver IC targeting wearable health and fitness devices, healthcare devices, smart watches, LTE mobile hotspots, bank keys, industrial applications, etc.

Large Display
- TFT Gate / Source LCD Driver for LCD TV, monitors, notebooks, etc.


Contact Person
Jessica Lee







