Solomon Systech Limited

- Hong Kong
				
				






























									
																			
						Established in July 1999, Solomon Systech is a leading fabless semiconductor company specialized in high quality semiconductor products which includes IC design, high voltage wafer process development, system application, new IC packaging design, IC test development, quality and supply chain management, sales and marketing of IC products.Solomon Systech technology has its core competence in Mixed Mode, High Voltage System-on-Chip (SoC) IC Development, which covers product design and intellectual property development. Its technology and technical know-how enable the company to turn new product ideas successfully into global commercial products.In four years time, Solomon Systech has developed and introduced many display driver/controller IC products in its own brand name for mobile phones, PDA, color LCD, and emerging new display such as OLED, microdisplay and e-paper. The products are also qualified and widely used by worldwide first tier telecommunication system manufacturers.With its recent success in OLED driver IC technology, Solomon Systech is transforming the mobile phone industry with high resolution, self-emissive video display and becomes the world leader in OLED driver IC market.Solomon Systech is one of the major display IC suppliers in the worldwide mobile phone market and will continue to invest into R&D of new technologies.
					
				





